data.description: Nestled in  North Fort Myers, this ground floor condo is the epitome of modern living and convenience. Boasting a comprehensive remodel, this residence exudes sophistication and style. Step inside and immediately notice the attention to detail, with brand-new kitchen cabinets and countertops that create a sleek, contemporary look. The pristine new flooring flows seamlessly throughout the spacious living areas, providing both beauty and durability. This condo offers a coveted split floor plan, ensuring privacy and comfort for all residents. Each generously sized bedroom boasts its own private bathroom, making it a haven for relaxation and convenience. The property comes complete with a designated parking spot, guaranteeing hassle-free parking for you and your guests. Conveniently situated close to I-75 and US 41, this condo allows easy access to the entire Fort Myers region, including shopping, dining, and recreational opportunities. But that's not all; this community provides an array of amenities to enhance your lifestyle. Take a dip in the inviting community pool, challenge your friends to a game of tennis on the courts, or try your hand at bocce ball for a fun outdoor experience
